!Type
!Icon
!Explanation
|-
|Performance Blocked
|[[File:Perf fallback verypoor.png|frameless|32x32px]]
[[File:Perf fallback poorAndBelow.png|frameless|32x32px]]
|Appears when the user's avatar exceeds a user's [[Special:MyLanguage/Settings#Avatar Optimization|Minimum Avatar Performance Rank]] set.
|-
|File Size Blocked
|[[File:Perf fallback fulldrive.png|frameless|32x32px]]
|Appears when the user's avatar exceeds the Maximum Allowed Avatar Download Size or Uncompressed Size you've set.
|-
|Impostor
|[[File:Perf fallback imposter.png|frameless|32x32px]]
|Appears when viewing the user's [[Special:MyLanguage/Impostors|impostor]].
|-
|Filtered
|[[File:Perf fallback filtered.png|frameless|32x32px]]
|Appears when the user's avatar gets filtered by [[Special:MyLanguage/Content Gating|Content Gating]].
|-
|Missing Asset
|[[File:Perf fallback missing.png|frameless|32x32px]]
|Appears when the user's avatar isn't available on your platform.
|-
|Error
|[[File:Perf fallback error.png|frameless|32x32px]]
|Appears when the user's avatar hasn't loaded due to an error.
